high_descs: Pick up the egg in the sink.
Bring the egg to the microwave.
Heat the egg in the microwave.
Bring the egg to the trash can.
Put the egg in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated egg in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the sink.
Pick the egg up that is in the sink.
With the egg go to the microwave and open the microwave door.
Put the egg in the microwave oven and shut the door.  Turn the microwave on.  When finished open the door and take the egg out of the microwave.  Shut the microwave door.
Go to the trash can that is on the left side of the fridge.
Put the egg in the trash can to the left and behind the object that is in there.
anns.task_desc: Warm up an egg to throw it away.

high_descs: turn right and head over to the kitchen sink at the right corner of the room
grab the egg out of the sink
turn left and head over to the microwave straight ahead
place the egg inside of the microwave, microwave it, then take it back out
move to the left a bit and face the garbage bin next to the fridge on the left
place the egg inside of the garbage bin
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved egg inside the garbage bin
